The paper discusses testing and analysis techniques for software applications, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. The focus is on collecting and processing data from the field, such as crash reports and profile data, which relates to computer security (cs.CR) and programming languages (cs.PL). The paper also mentions executing techniques directly in the field, which could fall under systems and control (cs.SY) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
